name: Swoosh Token
description:
he swoosh token is tied to the swoosh app.
The swoosh app will be a bridge between the end user and the content creator.
With the app, users will be able to donate money to their creator in the form of cryptos and also send a message.
the special thing about this is that the creator can reply directly to this message, giving the user a feeling of closeness to the creator, like you know it from whatsapp.
